headline: Flu Season  May Get Ugly Yet, Warns The C.D.C.
abstract: Almost as many people are falling ill as did two years ago, in what was a particularly severe flu season. But this season’s virus is unusual, and it’s too early to tell how dangerous.
lead_paragraph: The United States may be headed into a bad flu season, according to figures recently released by the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention.
keywords: Centers for Disease Control and Prevention
